@GardinerHarris told me on @LoomerUnleashed last night that Johnson & Johnson @JNJNews has known about the public health risks posed by Tylenol for DECADES, all while the FDA has looked the other way for Big Pharma checks. 

As a result, parents and kids have paid the price. According to Gardiner’s new book, 2.2 million Americans have been killed by Johnson and Johnson products, and they have never been held accountable.

